    "html" :
    
    
    "                         After working on wheel suspension parts, when replacing the steering-angle sensor, and after changing the wheel alignment values, calibrate the steering-angle sensor using the                          <b>PIWIS Tester</b>                         .                     "
    
    }
    
    }
    ,
    
    
    "Keep the front wheels in straight-ahead position on the measuring platform during calibration."
    ,
    
    
    "For vehicles with electromechanical steering, also re-teach the electric steering lock settings."
    
